    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="1-Hexo-NexT"><a href="#1-Hexo-NexT" class="headerlink" title="1. Hexo NexT"></a>1. Hexo NexT</h2><h3 id="1-1-Centered-Quote-引用"><a href="#1-1-Centered-Quote-引用" class="headerlink" title="1.1. Centered Quote 引用"></a>1.1. <a href="https://theme-next.js.org/docs/tag-plugins/#Centered-Quote">Centered Quote 引用</a></h3><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% cq %&#125;居中的引言&#123;% endcq %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

